        "content": "<p>Hello everyone, I was trying to prove Kepler's Law using Newtonian mechanics. Could you help me fill the sorry using tactics?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Data.Real.Sqrt</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Algebra.Algebra.Pi</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">Real</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">m_1</span> <span class=\"n\">m_2</span> <span class=\"n\">d_1</span> <span class=\"n\">d_2</span> <span class=\"n\">d</span> <span class=\"n\">w</span> <span class=\"n\">F_g</span> <span class=\"n\">F_c</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">m_1</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">d_1</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">m_2</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">d_2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Center of mass</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">d</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">d_1</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">d_2</span> <span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Distance between two bodies</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h3</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">F_g</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">m_1</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">m_2</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Gravitational Force</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h4</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">F_c</span><span class=\"bp\">=</span>  <span class=\"n\">m_2</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">d_2</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Centrifugal Force</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h5</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">F_c</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">F_g</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Force Balance</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h6</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">π</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Period definition</span>\n <span class=\"c1\">-- m_1&gt;0 , m_2&gt;0, d_1&gt;0, d_2&gt;0, p&gt;0 {Positivity constraints}</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h7</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">m_1</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h8</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">m_2</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h9</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">d_1</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h10</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">d_2</span> <span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h11</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span clas